title: 715. Players That Stood Out In Week 1 + College Programs with Most Players on NFL Rosters
itunes:title: 715. Players That Stood Out In Week 1 + College Programs with Most Players on NFL Rosters
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. On this special show, the guys start by discussing players that stood out in Week 1 of the NFL season. Next, the pair talk about college programs with the most players on active NFL Kickoff Weekend rosters. Then, the duo explain why one college football player has to tackle better.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
